{"id":1175,"date":"2025-04-11T00:10:07","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T17:10:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1175"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:39:17","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:39:17","slug":"seo-tca","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/seo-tca\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u1eb9o v\u1edbi TCA"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho s\u1eb9o Icepick scar (S\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng ch\u00e2n kim)<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eb9o ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1y nh\u1ecdn v\u00e0 s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 \u0111\u00e1y vu\u00f4ng h\u1eb9p.<\/li>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh Collagen, m\u1edd th\u00e2m, gi\u1ea3m s\u1eb9o, da s\u00e1ng m\u00e0u.<\/li>\n<li>Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhanh, \u00edt x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5m TCA c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1eb9o \u0111\u00e1y nh\u1ecdn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br \/>\nCh\u1ea5m TCA n\u1ed1t s\u1eb9o t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 l\u1ea7n (\u0110\u1ea1t frosting sau kho\u1ea3ng 10s).<\/li>\n<li>TCA Peel 20% to\u00e0n v\u00f9ng s\u1eb9o \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng frosting.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da s\u1eb9o t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, m\u1edd th\u00e2m, da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 2 ti\u1ebfng( tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eb9o)<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 \u2013 05 l\u1ea7n,<br \/>\nkho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n TCA kho\u1ea3ng 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho s\u1eb9o Icepick scar (S\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng ch\u00e2n kim)<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3536,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[33],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1175","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-peel","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1175","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1175"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3536"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1175"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1175"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1175"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=1175"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}